race.comment: SMOKIN REELS (2) will find this a little easier than his 1.5 lengths defeat on debut over 1200m at this track. Drawn close to the inside and has gate speed. Has been briefly freshened and is ready to win. ROCK ON ANGEL (8) switched from a NSW yard and was run over late well supported here off a 57-day break. Her Lismore placing prior stacks up and the 2kg claim is handy. She's a player with the extra fitness. NIVEN (1) keeps Wiggins and can build on his distant placing in the same race. Maps to get every chance. MIDDLE CHILD (7) started at $4.80 in the same contest but was only fair to the line. Has to run out a strong 1200m but a better effort is anticipated.
